research/history/operator_hints.json:4:    "message": "当前额外提示只有一条：不要再把主要预算投入到现有 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的局部扫参。若同一 family 连续多轮未形成新非支配点，下一轮优先切换到新的结构假设或新增最小可运行原型。",
research/history/operator_hints.json:15:    "message": "当前最值得补的新结构信息是异构 MoE：`shared experts + routed experts`，并优先考虑“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific head / local top-k”这类 expert 内部 low-rank 方案。不要把同质 `expert_topk ACTIVE_EXPERTS>1` 的负信号外推为对这条线的否定；应尽量做 matched-cost 对照，直接回答它是否优于当前 frontier 的已有点。",
research/history/patches/round_0027.patch:7:+| `expert_topk` | `x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i} b_{e,i}` | candidate | 轻量 router 只选择静态子库；激活路径仍是子库上的有限加权和 | 直接兼容 |
research/history/patches/round_0043.patch:7:+    "lowrank_expert_topk": _LOWRANK_KEYS,
research/history/patches/round_0043.patch:18:+| `lowrank_expert_topk` | `x_hat = Σ_r β_r u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i} b_{e,i}` | candidate | low-rank trunk 吃掉平滑主干，router 只选择静态 expert 子库，最终仍是静态库上的有限加权和 | 扩展兼容 |
